data.description: Welcome Home to this spacious ranch in Reynoldsburg. Upon entering, you will find a living room which features a double-sided woodburning fireplace complete with brick hearth. The kitchen boasts ceramic flooring and a walk-in pantry, seamlessly connecting to the dining space. The owner's bedroom offers an en suite, providing a private retreat. Two additional bedrooms give flexibility for guests, a home office, or a growing family. Ample natural light floods the interior through numerous windows, especially in the family room. Practical features include a 1-car garage with additional workshop area, ensuring space for storage and hobbies. A shed further complements the available storage options. Beautifully landscaped surroundings add to the curb appeal. Schedule your private showing today!
